    "image_with_text_pCbhLL": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_VbVgPi": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Premium Materials, Colours & Styles",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_VkEraJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Franke’s stainless steel sinks are crafted from high-grade, rust-resistant steel, offering exceptional durability and a sleek, contemporary finish. They’re easy to clean, hygienic, and withstand the heat and hustle of a busy Australian kitchen. Whether you need a single or double bowl, these sinks are designed to handle it all.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_VbVgPi",
        "text_VkEraJ"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/AM004_Epos_Berlin.jpg",
        "height": "adapt",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "text_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "top",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "mobile_content_alignment": "left",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_xWfRwf": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_UTidPf": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Granite & Composite Sinks",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_r7WXm6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>If you’re after a statement piece, consider Franke’s granite and composite sinks. Made from a blend of quartz and acrylic resins, these sinks are remarkably scratch-resistant and incredibly durable. Their natural stone-like texture provides an anti-bacterial surface, making them perfect for family kitchens. Choose from a range of colours—<a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-sinks?gf_72959=white\" title=\"White Franke Sinks\">white</a>, grey, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-sinks?gf_72959=black\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-sinks?gf_72959=black\">black</a>, and more—to complement any design theme.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_UTidPf",
        "text_r7WXm6"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/AM007_Mythos.jpg",
        "height": "small",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "image_first",
