        },
        "text_NbW3Jk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>    Ready to discover the perfect Franke sink for your home? Browse our complete <a href=\"/collections/franke\" title=\"Franke\">Franke range</a> or check out our extensive selection of  <a href=\"/collections/sinks\" title=\"Kitchen Sinks\">kitchen sinks</a>. Looking for expert tips on choosing the right materials or design inspiration for your next kitchen makeover? Explore our <a href=\"/blogs/news/kitchen-sink-size\" title=\"Choosing the Right Size and Configuration for Your Kitchen Sink\">Kitchen Sink Buying Guide</a> article from the News section, detailing considerations for selecting the perfect sink. For more design-focused ideas, check out our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/blogs/inspiration\" title=\"Inspiration Blogs\">Inspiration section</a>, where posts like    dive into current trends and styling tips to help elevate your culinary space.</p>"
